text: Habermann () is a 2010 Czech German Austrian war drama movie directed by Juraj Herz and starring Mark Waschke, Hannah Herzsprung, Wilson Gonzalez Ochsenknecht, Karel Roden, Franziska Weisz, Ben Becker, Andrej Hryc. ==Other websites== * Category:2010 drama movies Category:2010s war movies Category:Czech drama movies Category:German drama movies Category:Austrian drama movies Category:Movies directed by Juraj Herz
